# Learnova LMS тАУ Implementation Plan

Learnova is a web-based LMS built with **Next.js** (frontend), **Node.js + Express** (backend), **Prisma + Supabase PostgreSQL** (database), and **Supabase Auth + Storage**. This plan details all files to be created, organized by phase and component.

---

## Proposed Changes

---

### Phase 1 тАФ Project Setup

#### [NEW] `learnova-backend/` тАФ Express API Server
Scaffolded Node.js + Express + TypeScript project.

```
learnova-backend/
тФЬтФАтФА src/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА index.ts              тЖТ App entry, middleware, CORS
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА config/
тФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА env.ts            тЖТ Typed env vars (dotenv)
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА lib/
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА supabase.ts       тЖТ Supabase client (Auth + Storage)
тФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА prisma.ts         тЖТ Prisma client singleton
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА middleware/
тФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА auth.middleware.ts тЖТ Supabase JWT verification
тФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА rbac.middleware.ts тЖТ Role-based access control
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА routers/              тЖТ Feature routers (one per module)
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА services/             тЖТ Business logic layer
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА types/                тЖТ Shared TypeScript types
тФЬтФАтФА prisma/
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА schema.prisma         тЖТ Full DB schema
тФЬтФАтФА .env                      тЖТ SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, DATABASE_URL
тФФтФАтФА package.json
```

#### [NEW] `learnova-web/` тАФ Next.js Frontend
```
learnova-web/
тФЬтФАтФА app/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА (public)/             тЖТ Login, Register, Course Browse
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА (auth)/               тЖТ Dashboard, Learn, Quiz, Profile
