---

### Phase 2 тАФ Database Schema

#### [MODIFY] `prisma/schema.prisma`
Full schema covering all entities:

| Model | Key Fields |
|---|---|
| `User` | id, email, role (enum), full_name, total_points |
| `Course` | id, instructor_id, title, is_published, visibility |
| `Lesson` | id, course_id, content_type, content_url, order_index |
| `Quiz` | id, course_id, passing_score_pct, max_attempts |
| `Question` | id, quiz_id, type (enum), points |
| `Option` | id, question_id, text, is_correct |
| `Enrollment` | user_id + course_id (unique pair) |
| `Progress` | user_id + lesson_id, is_completed, video_position |
| `QuizAttempt` | id, user_id, quiz_id, score_pct, passed |
| `Review` | user_id + course_id, rating (1тАУ5), comment |
| `Badge` | id, name, type, threshold |
| `UserBadge` | user_id + badge_id (unique pair) |
| `Certificate` | id, user_id, course_id, certificate_uid |

---

### Phase 3 тАФ Authentication

#### [NEW] `src/middleware/auth.middleware.ts`
- Verifies incoming Supabase JWT via `supabase.auth.getUser(token)`
- Attaches `req.user` (id, email, role) to request

#### [NEW] `src/middleware/rbac.middleware.ts`
- `requireRole(...roles)` factory тАФ returns 403 if role not allowed

#### [NEW] `app/(public)/login/page.tsx`
- Supabase `signInWithPassword` client call
- Redirect to dashboard on success

#### [NEW] `app/(public)/register/page.tsx`
- Supabase `signUp` + insert into `users` table via backend
- Email confirmation flow

