## Verification Plan

> This is a new codebase тАФ no existing tests to run. Verification will be manual via browser and API client (Postman / Thunder Client).

### Manual Verification Steps

**Auth**
1. Open app тЖТ register a new account тЖТ confirm in Supabase Dashboard under Auth > Users
2. Login тЖТ verify JWT token set in browser cookie/session
3. Try accessing `/studio` as a Learner role тЖТ confirm 403

**Course Creation**
4. Login as Instructor тЖТ create a course тЖТ add 3 lessons (1 video URL, 1 PDF, 1 text)
5. Publish course тЖТ confirm it appears in public course listing

**Learning Flow**
6. Login as Learner тЖТ enroll in course тЖТ open lesson player
7. Complete all lessons тЖТ verify progress bar reaches 100%
8. Confirm certificate appears on profile

**Quiz Flow**
9. Instructor creates a 3-question quiz on the course
10. Learner submits quiz тЖТ verify score, points awarded, result screen shown
11. Submit same quiz again тЖТ verify reduced points on 2nd attempt

**Gamification**
12. Check dashboard for points total and badge level after quiz submission
13. Manually set total_points in Supabase Dashboard to a badge threshold тЖТ verify badge awarded

**Reporting**
14. Login as Instructor тЖТ open course analytics тЖТ verify learner count, completion %, avg score
15. Click export тЖТ verify CSV download contains correct data

**API via Postman**
- `POST /api/v1/auth/login` тЖТ 200 + token
- `GET /api/v1/courses` тЖТ 200 + list
- `POST /api/v1/quizzes/:id/submit` with valid body тЖТ 200 + result
- Unauthorized request тЖТ 401
- Wrong role тЖТ 403
